      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">君子于役.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>君子于役，不知其期。曷至哉？雞棲于塒，日之夕矣，羊牛下來。君子于役，如之何勿思！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My husband is away on service,
Not knowing the day of his return.
When the sheep and oxen come down from the hill,
How can I not think of him?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
