      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">君子于役.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>君子于役，不日不月。曷其有佸？雞棲于桀，日之夕矣，羊牛下括。君子于役，苟無飢渴。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My husband is away on service,
Not knowing the day of his return.
When the fowls roost in the evening,
How can I not think of him?</seg>
      </tuv>
